Body: What is the SilkLife?   SilkLife is a decentralized, mutually-trusted and encouraging cross-border life community that is protected through blockchain technology, bound by smart contracts and furnished with a TOKEN incentive mechanism and mutual evaluation mechanism.  SilkLife focuses on application scenarios including Overseas travel, shopping, healthcare and study. Silk Branches across the world have connected hotels, retailers, schools, medical institutions, scenic spot operators to the SilkLife ecosystem, which recommends directly to global customers. Meanwhile, the blockchain technology-based autonomous commercial smart contract (SC application) can make the contract performance, payment and responsibility recognition process in traditional service trade become intelligent. In addition, SC application is absolutely decentralized and cannot be falsified, as it’s based on blockchain technology. Disputes in service trade can be arbitrated through decentralized social group forces, which in turn guarantees interests of contractual parties in a smart manner. Many buyers of Silk ecological community are ready to experience.  Now, the SilkOne financial services system is currently in development. We held Business Promotion Conferences and invited buyers to apply for a loan line of credit. Buyers who apply early will enjoy the interest deduction. After product testing and service process improvement, we will gradually open financial services to buyers from Silk ecological community throughout Indonesia and southeast Asia. After the buyback of Silk, it is destroyed on a monthly basis. The service is expected to became popular in Indonesia. It will promote, maintain and enhance the value of Silk Token. Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: SilkChain:Outline of Secondary Incubation Solution for Local Brands   Producers can provide samples in small amounts and identify target market, so as to target local trade nodes and provide them with rewarding Silk Token. Trade nodes can provide offline shops locally and sell samples at affordable prices in their consumer communities. Local consumers that purchase the samples will be rewarded with Token, while they are expected to give sincere comments on the functions, packaging and brand design of the products. The SilkChain will automatically record the comments received as well as the basic information of the consumers（excluding personal sensitive information but including dimension information） on the chain so as to provide references for service providers to analyze the consumers’ responses on the samples. Other third parties can provide their services during the entire process such as organizing chambers of commerce, promotions and marketing activities, and all response they provide will be rewarded with Token. Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: The Eco-city of Silk Attracts Participants of Global Trade to Join the SilkChain   The Eco-city of Silk isa social system based on blockchain technology to improve the ecology of international trade and cross-border consumption. Adhering to the principle of decentralization, openness and win-win, the Eco-city of Silk attracts participants of global trade to join the SilkChainthrough the incentive design, circulation design and various incentive applications. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: DZ Becomes the Super Node and Silk Supply Chain Service Center is Officially Opened   At present, the products in the international trade, especially among SMEs, are produced by the world’s factory China. Due to factors like the slackening global economy in recent years and the trade war between China and the United States, many foreign trade companies are faced with more difficulties than before. They begin to seek more trustworthy orders from other markets apart form that of the developed countries. They are eager to gain the product feedback from overseas markets at a low cost and trade with credible wholesalers.  As the first blockchain project dedicated to improving international trade and consumer spending ecosystem, SilkChain are trying to solve this problem. Now, a Chinese County-level Luggage and Bag Industry Association — DZ has passed the verification and shall become the first super node of SilkChain in China. DZ can through Silk to enter the local market in Indonesia with SilkChain resources and solve the problems of local logistics, marketing channels and e-commerce platforms. This also marks that the SilkChain began to occupy the Indonesian luggage and bag wholesale market.  About Silk Node — DZ  DZ is composed of a county-level luggage and bag manufacturing enterprise and related enterprises in China, and has more than 50 member units. Facing the unpredictable international trade, DZ will cooperate with SilkChain in all aspects.  On the one hand, Silk Node — DZ opens up the Indonesian market through SilkChain resources and lands in the wholesale service center — Indobags Wholesale in the largest local wholesale Market — Tanah Abang Market. At the same time, the center is also the officially authorized Silk Supply Chain Service Center. Recently, the center has officially opened. Through the service center, whether the local SMS wholesalers or terminal buyers hoping to reduce the cost of procurement in Indonesia, can find cooperation with Silk as the settlement currency or medium of exchange.  On the other hand, DZ will work together with SilkChain in Silk Tokenization project to establish the e-commerce platform IndoBags, which endows offline entities for e-commercialization. SilkChain implants Silk with blockchain technology, which provides better service for customers. Meanwhile, SilkChain’s ecosystem is constantly expanding and flourishing.  Hundreds of super nodes for different industries are planned by SilkChain. We are looking forward to every participant of international trade as trading companies, platforms, shopping malls, and cross-border e-commerce enterprises to join the SILK Super Node Election for more benefits of the SilkChain ecosystem.  SilkChain will focus on super node and update every progress, please stay tuned! Body: Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center will be Established which is Expected to Service 300 Super Nodes   Since SilkChain has launched SILK Super Node Election, there are 20 nodes have passed the first stage application. At present, PT Paloma Shopway has passed the verification and shall become the first super node, Silk Node — Paloma. To support more and more enterprises joining in the SILK Super Node Election and service super nodes or nodes, SilkChain team will establish Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center in this month after the preparation of dozens of day in Indonesia.  Indonesia Tanah Abang Market  Indonesia is the important Belt-and-Road country, which has a population of 250 million huge markets, but also the world’s fourth largest consumer market. There are a lot of wholesale markets in the Indonesian capital Jakarta. One of the main textiles Tanah Abang Market is the largest and oldest of the markets. Tanah Abang Market is Southeast Asia’s largest textile and clothing wholesale center which has 13000 stalls for accommodating 75000 shoppers at the same time. There are thousands of products such as the Muslim clothing, jeans, batik, bags and shoes and other goods.  SilkChain Will Establish Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center Near a Large Market  Facing considerable potential of emerging markets, SilkChain team had made a field study in Indonesia for several weeks, and decided to establish Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center near Indonesia’s largest clothing wholesale center — Tanah Abang Market. And SilkChain has established Silk Supply Chain Service Center in the market to better develop the Indonesian market with SilkChain ecological partners. At present, the team’s office is located in Cyber 2 Tower. Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center will be established soon. Through the Service Center, whether the local SMS wholesalers and buyers hoping to reduce the cost of procurement in Indonesia, or the manufacturers of international supply chains who want to export to Indonesia market, can find cooperation with Silk as the settlement currency or medium of exchange.  The Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center Improves the Circulation of Silk  The Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center has two main purposes: on the one hand, it helps SilkChain team to promote supers node or nodes in Indonesia. On the other hand, The Center provides a convenient and efficient trade platform for businesses, franchisees and global supply chain factories. For Indonesian businesses and franchisees, they can better understand the SilkChain through the Center, become the super nodes or nodes of SilkChain, and quickly find the products with lower price to reduce the purchase cost. For global supply chain factories who want to expand the market in Indonesia, they can through the Center to enter the local market in Indonesia with SilkChain resources and solve the problems of local logistics, marketing channels and e-commerce platforms. In order to improve the circulation of Silk, SilkChain implants Silk in Paloma commercial ecosystem with blockchain technology and innovates new business models, to help build the blockchain business ecosystem. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: Through Silk a Cross-Border Direct Purchase of Half Million RMB Has Been Facilitated for the First Time by Silk Node -Paloma   The global SMEs are not only numerous, but also have a tremendous amount of orders every year, which reaches two hundred thousand dollars ($200,000). However, current cross-border trades of SMEs from factories to merchants involve a number of middlemen, which not only increases the intermediary costs, but also blocks the communication between merchants in face of end consumers and factory product design.  As the first blockchain project dedicated to improving international trade and consumer spending ecosystem, SilkChain has launched the model of Silk Selection. It means we provide a way of cross-border direct purchase for overseas small and medium-sized buyers to help them to purchase directly from the Chinese small and medium-sized factories.  To Shorten the Supply Chain for Low Price is the Core-Value of Cross-Border Direct Purchase  SilkChain has completed the initial integration of the supply chain as well as the connection between the centralized procurement center of Chinese manufacturers and global large-scale commercial nodes, especially the Belt-and-Road countries. We are going to create a powerful and open-source community of mutual trust. In different trading activities, each community member can be either a service receiver or a service provider.  For example, by the recruitment plans of Silk Selection, a Chinese small factory joining the SilkChain ecosystem, he can log suppler management center to launch product information. After completing the order, the goods of factory will be sent to the Selection Preparatory Office, and by the freight transport company, goods will be sent to all over the world. In addition, suppliers can sell the goods directly to overseas small and medium-sized buyers and terminal clients in super node’s Selection platform. The biggest characteristic of this model is that due to greatly shorten the supply chain, the price is reduced greatly.  Through Silk the First Order of Half Million RMB Has Been Facilitated by Silk Node — Paloma  Now through Silk Selection platform, Silk Node–Paloma has ordered luggage goods worth 500,000 RMB from the Chinese factory, and paid portion Silk Token bought from the secondary market (HitBTC trading platform). This also indicates that Paloma has realized the introduction of Silk in commercial ecosystem with blockchain technology for improving the circulation of Silk.  SilkChain tries to solve several of pain points in this industry and build a “global blockchain free trade zone” technically by applying the blockchain technology. In free trade zones, SilkChain provides the bottom blockchain infrastructure and its Token system is introduced as the benchmark of value transmissions in trade activities between small and medium-sized merchants. Overseas small and medium-sized buyers can make the cross-border direct purchase with silk for purchasing directly from the Chinese small and medium-sized factories. Without middlemen, overseas small and medium-sized buyers will reduce procurement costs, the factories will make more profits and consumers will get more affordable prices.  SilkChain will launch Paloma series and update every progress, please stay tuned! Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: SilkPay — A Global Crypto Currency Payment Service Platform   SilkChain is the first project in the world that dedicates blockchain technology to improving international trade and consumer spending ecology. In order to make trade economy tokenized, SilkChain has launched the Silk Tokenization for global commodity cities, traders and trade service providers.  The SilkChain global enterprises Silk Tokenization is a lightweight blockchain improvement of traditional enterprises in payment, transfer, account management and cross-chain asset management through Dapp applications, digital wallets, smart contract templates customized by SilkChain. Meanwhile, it can also have the services of software customization, low-cost marketing, as well as the finance of supply chains and consumption. Additionally, it uses the fundamental SDK, API and middleware to provide customized blockchain applications for mature companies. All of those can be supplied by third-party service companies that are introduced by SilkChain.  Based on Silk, SilkPay is a global crypto currency payment service platform, providing crypto currency payment for global users. Users can complete crypto currency payment and settlement with SilkPay. It is dedicated to meeting the lightweight blockchain improvement needs of ecological partners for payment and transfer. To build community prosperity, SilkPay will improve the $12 trillion SMEs cross-border trade payment market.  About SilkPay  SilkPay is the global leader online payment platform. Its core members are from senior Internet payment industries and operation of international e-commerce enterprises. With a complete risk prevention mechanism, SilkPay has rich experience in payment operation and management.  SilkPay provides convenient electronic payment service to meet the worldwide demand of customers. Such as crypto currency payment, global bank cable transfer and payment gateway.  Transfer service of SilkPay is fast and efficient of which the fees are lower than that of traditional transfer service, and its digital cryptography is more secure.  The Four Advantages of SilkPay  1. Payment  Customers can pay Silk online or offline via SilkPay to merchants.  2. Currency Converter  It supports the legal tender price, payment of crypto currency as well as the settlement of crypto currency.  3. Recharge  Customers can transfer crypto currency to SilkPay wallet address.  4. Withdraw  SilkPay allows users to withdraw Silk to their wallet address.  The Development of SilkPay  In August 2018, SilkPay was officially launched.  In September 2018, the development of SilkPay third-party one-step payment application was completed and officially launched.Users can turn on or off the one-step payment function online.  Since SilkPay was officially launched less than two months ago, nearly 30 Dapps have applied for SilkPay service, among which six have been approved and used.  Currently SilkPay has opened developer functions to Dapp within the SilkChain ecosystem, providing Silk online collection, recharge and withdrawal functions for Dapp. After online application for developer functions, Dapps can download developer documents for developing SilkPay and enjoy online payment service. Body: Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center will be Established which is Expected to Service 300 Super Nodes   Since SilkChain has launched SILK Super Node Election, there are 20 nodes have passed the first stage application. At present, PT Paloma Shopway has passed the verification and shall become the first super node, Silk Node — Paloma. To support more and more enterprises joining in the SILK Super Node Election and service super nodes or nodes, SilkChain team will establish Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center in this month after the preparation of dozens of day in Indonesia.  Indonesia Tanah Abang Market  Indonesia is the important Belt-and-Road country, which has a population of 250 million huge markets, but also the world’s fourth largest consumer market. There are a lot of wholesale markets in the Indonesian capital Jakarta. One of the main textiles Tanah Abang Market is the largest and oldest of the markets. Tanah Abang Market is Southeast Asia’s largest textile and clothing wholesale center which has 13000 stalls for accommodating 75000 shoppers at the same time. There are thousands of products such as the Muslim clothing, jeans, batik, bags and shoes and other goods.  SilkChain Will Establish Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center Near a Large Market  Facing considerable potential of emerging markets, SilkChain team had made a field study in Indonesia for several weeks, and decided to establish Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center near Indonesia’s largest clothing wholesale center — Tanah Abang Market. And SilkChain has established Silk Supply Chain Service Center in the market to better develop the Indonesian market with SilkChain ecological partners. At present, the team’s office is located in Cyber 2 Tower. Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center will be established soon. Through the Service Center, whether the local SMS wholesalers and buyers hoping to reduce the cost of procurement in Indonesia, or the manufacturers of international supply chains who want to export to Indonesia market, can find cooperation with Silk as the settlement currency or medium of exchange.  The Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center Improves the Circulation of Silk  The Silk Super Node Franchisee Service Center has two main purposes: on the one hand, it helps SilkChain team to promote supers node or nodes in Indonesia. On the other hand, The Center provides a convenient and efficient trade platform for businesses, franchisees and global supply chain factories. For Indonesian businesses and franchisees, they can better understand the SilkChain through the Center, become the super nodes or nodes of SilkChain, and quickly find the products with lower price to reduce the purchase cost. For global supply chain factories who want to expand the market in Indonesia, they can through the Center to enter the local market in Indonesia with SilkChain resources and solve the problems of local logistics, marketing channels and e-commerce platforms. In order to improve the circulation of Silk, SilkChain implants Silk in Paloma commercial ecosystem with blockchain technology and innovates new business models, to help build the blockchain business ecosystem. Body: Silk Node — Suntex Has Ordered Luggage and Bags through Silk and Establishes Own Brand JC LEWIS Recently, Suntex Jclewis International Inc has passed the verification of ITDC and shall become the second super node, Silk Node — Suntex. Suntex was dedicated to the developments and sales of offline chain stores in the Philippines. Suntex has entered e-commercial field and cooperated closely with LAZADA and SHOPEE, the two biggest e-commerce platforms in Philippine.  Establish the Luggage and Bag Brand — JC LEWIS and Finish the Cross-Border Trade Directly  SilkChain has completed the initial integration of the supply chain as well as the connection between the centralized procurement center of Chinese manufacturers and global large-scale commercial nodes, especially in the Belt-and-Road countries. Now through Silk, Silk Node — Suntex has ordered bulk luggage and bags from Chinese factory, and establishes the luggage and bag brand — JC LEWIS. Because cross-border direct purchase has been realized, they reduce procurement costs without middlemen. At the same time, they will make use of the local resource advantages of the Philippines to prosper the Silk ecological community and maximize the benefits.  This order for customized samples are from 13 Chinese suppliers recommended by Silk Selection, including 206 handbags, fanny packs, coin purses and satchels. At present, they have been sent to Manila, the capital of the Philippines.  Establish Suntex Selection to Enter the E-commercial Field  Suntex has entered e-commercial field and cooperated closely with LAZADA and SHOPEE, the two biggest e-commerce platforms in Philippine, which mainly sell products of various brands. To enter fully the e-commercial field, Silk Node — Suntex will work together with SilkChain in Silk Tokenization project to establish the local B2B e-commerce platform Suntex Selection in the Philippines and explore supplier resources from various categories in e-commerce platform and complete the implementation of e-commercial supply chain through goods selection and payment of Suntex Selection. Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: The Official Demonstration Project of SilkChain Ecological Community Super Node -Silk Selection has been Launched  The official demonstration project of SilkChain ecological community super node -Silk Selection has been launched on October 29, 2018. The platform enables users to exchange Silk points and buy goods on Silk Selection.    Click on the following link to download and the link is  http://selection.silkchain.net About Silk Selection  Silk Selection is an online and offline service channel established by ITDC, which connects market, factory direct purchase and global SME buyers. It also integrates business matching platform, cross-border financial service of supply chain, the source factory procurement management services, de-intermediated AD marketing services, cross-border trading services, to form an intelligent blockchain trading platform.Meanwhile, the incentive points mechanism of cross-border ecological construction is introduced in Silk Selection, which also records society, business and transaction behaviors of cross-border business and uses Silk to empower community economy, more active and more incentives. At the same time, Silk Selection enables users to exchange Silk points to purchase goods.  About Odoor  Based on SilkChain ecosystem, Odoor is the world’s first blockchain advertising market platform. Any organization or individual can advertise on the platform. Odoor is also a win-win platform where all participants are rewarded. Not only can users earn Silk from reading advertisements, but also the advertising revenue of the platform will be distributed to all participants of the SilkChain ecosystem. In Odoor, users can get rewards through clicking, reading, sharing, comments and other user behaviors (more than six ways).  How to Earn Silk in Odoor  1. Users can get a reward from sharing link after it is clicked by others.  2. Every time you invite a user to read an advertisement, the reward will go to your account according to a certain percentage. You can get a reward from the total reading income of 1st level, 2nd level and 3rd level friends, as follows:  Friend level:   1st level      2nd level         3rd level Income ratio:     15%           9%                   6%  For example, each of you invited a friends from the “odoor” registered SilkChain and complete the KYC authentication, and you can get 30 Silk awards. There is no limit to the number of invitations.  When you invite Jack to visit “Odoor”, Jack gets 20 Silk for reading the ad and deposits it to his SilkChain account, you will get 20 * 15% = 3 Silk; Jack invites Mary, who earns 20 Silk for reading and deposits it to her SilkChain account, you will get 20 * 9% = 1.8 Silk.Welcome to Join Odoor  As a commercial platform, Odoor is able to bring considerable flow and opportunities to the publishers, and make SilkChain members closer. Organizations and individuals from all sectors can pay Silk for advertisement, promotion, cooperation etc. At present, Odoor has successfully cooperated with Silk Selection, SilkAll and one of China’s well-known 3D printing vertical media-3DHOO to share the huge dividend of ecological development.  In the future, as more new modules and functions are introduced to Odoor, there will be more people entering it to publish or read. In this way, Odoor will break the traditional advertising model and build a new blockchain advertising market platform of the new products promotion from various industries which will provide better experience to community members. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: SilkChain has Launched SILK Super Node Election   In order to achieve community prosperity and share the huge dividends brought about by ecological development, as well as establish the value system of Silk, SilkChain has launched SILK Super Node Election. Details are as follows:  1. Definition  The SILK super nodes are the high-level benefit owners of SilkChain’s ecosystem. In the mean time, the SILK super nodes are responsible to expanding the community, boosting the ecosystem, and improving the liquidation of Silk tokens. Applicators for becoming a SILK super node shall be mature enterprises or organizations with 3,000,000 Silk tokens purchased from the secondary market and hold for long-term. Hundreds of super nodes for different industries are planned by SilkChain.  2. Benefits  2.1 Free software + termed operation & maintenance service  The super node will have the ownership of different application software and rights of profit share of such.  2.2 Self-owned Community bonus share  The super node will have rights of sharing the Silk gas fee and the profit share of self-owned community operation.  What is the self-owned community? SilkChain has tailored independent platforms for each super node. Subject to this platform, there are Silk applications such as e-commerce, financing, gadget, as well as entertainment. Any user linked to these applications belongs to the self-owned community of that super node.  2.3 Extra bonus  When the applicator purchased Silk tokens from the public, the applicator will be rewarded with locked Silk tokens as a bonus at certain rates. The rate and unlock terms are related to the whole amount of the applicators holding tokens.  2.4 Task bonus  The super nodes will be rewarded with task bonuses at each milestone of task completion.  2.5 Referral bonus  The super nodes will be rewarded with referral bonus by succeeding introducing other applicators for super nodes.  2.6 Massive business opportunity  The super node will share massive information of suppliers and products for developing potential business in the SilkChain ecosystem.  3. Rights  3.1 Ownership of free software  3.2 Permission rights of subject nodes’ entry.  4. Decision-making Mechanism  Every Silk super node has the voting rights for adding & revising the mechanism, terms, and regulations of the Silk super nodes. Before the existence of 30 SILK super nodes, the International Trade Digitalization Commission (ITDC) has the final decision-making rights. After that, a decision-making committee will be elected under negotiation & voting of 30 SILK super nodes under supervision of ITDC and all members of the SilkChain ecosystem for each decision-making.  At present, there are 20 nodes have passed the first stage application. Among which, PT. Paloma Shopway has passed the verification and shall become the first super node, Silk Node — Paloma and execute with the rights and responsibilities of a super node very soon. Established in 2007, PT. Paloma Shopway is the largest home catalogue distributor with 340,000 memberships across Indonesia, covering the market of 10 millions of people and has annual turnover of USD 100 million.  Furthermore, 3 recognized enterprises has passed the final verification and queuing for becoming a SILK super node and 16 applicators are under verification successively. We are looking forward to every participant of international trade as trading companies, platforms, shopping malls, and cross-border e-commerce enterprises to join the SILK Super Node Election for more benefits of the SilkChain ecosystem.  If there is any update or change of SILK Super Node Election, SilkChain will be noticed on the three official channels: SilkChain Website, SilkAll Service Groups and Official Telegram Groups. Stay Tuned! Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: The Official Demonstration Project of SilkChain Ecological Community Super Node -Silk Selection Will be Launched Soon  In order to build an equal and mutually beneficial international trade ecology and achieve community prosperity, as well as improve the circulation of Silk tokens, SilkChain will build Silk blockchain commercial network community through the global construction of Silk super nodes, attracting more global suppliers, distributors and service providers to join and become nodes on Silk blockchain, and gradually select the powerful and scale nodes as the Super Nodes.Then SilkChain will launch Silk Selection soon. Details are as follows:    1. Definition  Silk Selection is an online and offline service channel established by ITDC, which connects market, factory direct purchase and global SME buyers. It also integrates business matching platform, cross-border financial service of supply chain, the source factory procurement management services, de-intermediated AD marketing services, cross-border trading services, to form an intelligent blockchain trading platform.    Meanwhile, the incentive points mechanism of cross-border ecological construction is introduced in Silk Selection, which also records society, business and transaction behaviors of cross-border business and uses Silk to empower community economy, more active and more incentives. Finally, to help the global small and medium-sized enterprises direct factory purchasing docking, at the same time we provide trade financing services, achieving the dream of becoming a global business without leaving home.    Silk Selection as the first e-commerce demonstration application using the Silk blockchain technology, is for providing free series of commerce systems, incentive systems, and business entertainment systems to business super nodes who are willing to join in, as well as promoting the entrance of more merchants at a low cost to accelerate the expansion of service nodes around the world.    2. Clients  Global commodity suppliers, terminal purchases, consumers, and third party service organization.    3. The Service Module Included in Silk Selection  3.1 Content Distribution Service Module  Through the Silk Selection, global commodity suppliers can directly publish various commodity and service information to global terminal purchases and consumers. For example, through advertising, paid reading and other ways to establish interaction with customers, and get customer feedback on products, inquiry information, order consumption and other information.    3.2 Advertisement Marketing Service Module  Odoor is embedded in the Silk Selection, a decentralized advertising marketing module based on blockchain technology. Merchants can post ads on various social platforms to facilitate order transactions.    3.3 Commodity Distribution Comprehensive Service Module  Silk Selection provides one-stop service of international trade for commodity suppliers, including community interaction, commodity distribution, three-party logistics, transaction guarantee and financial business.    3.4 Business-SNS Service Module  Through the cooperation with various application partners of business ecological construction, the points system can be circulated within the platform, and the third-party application access platform can be supported to provide more business social service activities and incentive places for customers, so as to create a highly active ecological system for customers on the platform.    We are looking forward to every participant of international trade as global commodity suppliers, terminal purchases, consumers, and third party service organization to experience the Silk Selection, learn about Silk blockchain business and join as soon as possible to become a super node with own selection for improving international trade and consumer spending ecosystem.    Recently the first super node partner Silk Node - Paloma will launch Paloma Selection, as the first super node application open to the public. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: Attention! SilkChain has Launched Ecological Dividend Program!  In order to achieve community prosperity and share the huge dividends brought about by ecological development, SilkChain has launched ecological dividend program to give back to each community member in the ecology. Now, the ecological dividend is detailed:  1. Definition  1.1 Ecological Dividend  Ecological dividend is that all kinds of participants in the ecology have made outstanding contributions to the prosperity of SilkChain ecosystem during the construction process of SilkChain ecosystem. SilkChain will pay dividends to token holders according to the agreement in the white paper.  1.2 Token Holder  Token holder is the holding available Silk (unfrozen) KYC users in the SilkChain official wallet.  1.3 SilkChain Global Enterprises Silk Tokenization  The Silk Tokenization is a lightweight blockchain improvement of traditional enterprises through Dapp applications, digital wallets, smart contract templates customized by SilkChain. Meanwhile, it can also have the services of software customization, low-cost marketing, as well as the finance of supply chains and consumption. Additionally, it uses the fundamental SDK, API and middle ware to provide customized blockchain applications for mature companies. All of those can be supplied by third-party service companies that are introduced by SilkChain.  2. Two Main Sources of Silk Token Pools  2.1 SilkChain Ecological Operation Silk Token Pools  That is, the ecology of SilkChain has generated various economic benefits from various economic activities. SilkChain extracts Silk in proportion according to the agreed proportion as ecological operation Silk token pools.  2.2 Dapp Implementation Dividend Pool of SilkChain Global Enterprises Silk Tokenization  When traditional enterprises and traders who have joined in Global Silk Tokenization buy Silk Tokens from exchanges, after that, a certain proportion of the Silk Tokens will be collected to the Dapp application dividend pools.  3. Ecological Dividend Program  3.1 Operation Dividend Program  All kinds of income generated by various economic activities in SilkChain ecosystem will have corresponding incentive mechanism of distribution to each Token holder. With the continuous development and expansion of the ecosystem, the income categories will continue to be added. At present, the operation dividend to be launched include advertising application income, entertainment application income, e-commerce application income, SilkChain Gas dividend, etc. Besides, the operation dividend program is derived from the various economic benefits generated by the economic activities of the cross-border trade and cross-border consumer applications in the Silk community.  a) Advertising Application Income Odoor, the world’s first decentralized advertising platform based on blockchain, will distribute the profits of such platforms to all participants in the SilkChain ecosystem. SilkChain used 5% of the advertising revenue as the Silk token pools to reward each token holder.  b) Entertainment Application Income It is based on SilkAll’s turnover commissions of entertainment applications, of which 20% of turnover commissions will feed back to Silk members.  c) E-commerce Application Income It is based on SilkAll’s turnover commissions of e-commerce applications, mainly from consumption, of which 20% of turnover commissions will feed back to Silk members.  d) SilkChain Gas Dividend Silk of SilkChain ecological is transferred between users and applications through SilkPay. SilkChain will officially charge a certain amount of Silk as the Gas cost of SilkChain. SilkChain, meanwhile, pays out as much as 20% of the cost of Gas to Silk members.  e) The operation dividend program is derived from the various economic benefits generated by the economic activities of the cross-border trade and cross-border consumer applications in the Silk community.  3.2 Dapp Application Dividend Plan of Silk Tokenization  The partners such as traditional companies and traders in participation of Global Silk Tokenization are required to buy Silk Token in amount of US dollar 30,000–150,000 in public exchanges and hold for a long term so that they can enjoy the benefits of the traffic, transaction, supply chain as well as the services of software and big data for free, which are all brought by Silk Tokenization. In addition, these partners can constantly get free operation services of ecological Dapp provided by SilkChain. Meanwhile, these partners will provide a certain proportion of silk as dividends of Dapp implementation to reward the users in Silk Ecosystem.  Since SilkChain’s operation, it achievements in various fields are inseparable from the support and trust of community members. Therefore, SilkChain launched ecological incentive program to return the Silk members. At the same time, we also hope that all kinds of international enterprises can actively participate in the cooperation of Silk Tokenization for more ecological dividends of Silk, such as import and export trading companies, international global commodity cities and trading platforms, cross-border e-commerce enterprises.  If there is any update or change of the dividend program, SilkChain will be noticed on the three official channels: SilkChain Website, SilkAll Service Groups and Official Telegram Groups. Stay Tuned! Body: The New User Reward Program Updates  In order to build equal and mutually beneficial international trade ecology, achieve community prosperity, and share the huge dividends of ecological development with community users in a better way, SilkChain has updated the New User Reward Program. The Rules & Regulations are as follows:  1. To Get Rewards by Inviting New Users to SilkCommunity  Old user invites their friends to download registration and log in SilkAll (necessary steps). When new users log in and complete real name authentication (KYC authentication), new and old users can be rewarded, and old user (A) can be rewarded from new users (B, C, D). Real Name Authentication (KYC authentication) Reward  Old user invites their friends to real name authentication (KYC authentication). After successful authentication, new and old users can be rewarded, and old user (A) can be rewarded from new users (B, C, D). For example, A invites B, B invites C and C invites D, after D completes real name authentication (KYC authentication), A, B, C and D can get the incentives;  3. SilkAll Computing Power Award  Old user invites their friends to download registration and log in SilkAll. When new users log in for the first time and complete real name authentication (KYC authentication), old users can get computing power award, and old user (A) can be rewarded from new users (B, C, D). For example, A invites B, B invites C and C invites D, after the successful authentication (KYC authentication) of user D, C can get 50 power, B can get 20 power, A can get 10 power.  The above New User Rewards are available only after new users complete real name authentication (KYC authentication), then old users will get corresponding rewards. Body: Paloma Selection of Application Dividend Plan Will be Opened in SilkAll Soon   In order to show our gratitude to all users for their support and participation, SilkChain has launched the Dapp application dividend plan of global enterprises Silk Tokenization. In this plan, partners will provide a certain proportion of Silk as Dapp implementation dividend pool to reward the token holders（that is, the holding available Silk (unfrozen) KYC users in the SilkChain official wallet) in Silk Ecosystem. Paloma Selection of application dividend plan will be opened on October 10, 2018 at 10:00 AM, details as follows:  Paloma Selection Total: 120,000 Silk Number: 1500 Date: 2018–10–10  About Paloma Selection  Paloma Selection is a blockchain innovation project of PT Paloma Shopway in Indonesia. Founded in 2007, Paloma is the largest distribution company with home catalog tiered sales system. Paloma has set up a direct-selling network in Indonesia, which has about 340,000 members. Paloma covers a market about tens of millions Indonesian, and its annual sales are more than 100 million dollars.  SilkChain implants Silk in Paloma commercial ecosystem with blockchain technology. Paloma members can earn Silk by online shopping, consumption and product reviews. At the same time, they can use Silk to participate VIP sales promotion, such as integral redemption, getting prizes, lottery and etc. Paloma can obtain big data through Silk’s circulation in system, and build the Southeast Asian consumer credit system. Based on the establishment of the credit system, SilkFinance service offers trade finance and any other supply-chain financial services, to help build the blockchain business ecosystem.  All KYC users of SilkChain Ecosystem can apply for the qualification of airdrop. The application dividend plan of Paloma Selection is 120,000 Silk, available members are 1500. Welcome to pay attention to the application dividend plan of Paloma Selection. Seats are limited, first come first served.  At the same time, SilkChain also hopes that all kinds of international enterprises can actively participate in the cooperation of Silk Tokenization for more ecological dividends of Silk, such as import and export trading companies, international global commodity cities and trading platforms, cross-border e-commerce enterprises. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: SilkChain has Launched SILK Super Node Election   In order to achieve community prosperity and share the huge dividends brought about by ecological development, as well as establish the value system of Silk, SilkChain has launched SILK Super Node Election. Details are as follows:  1. Definition  The SILK super nodes are the high-level benefit owners of SilkChain’s ecosystem. In the mean time, the SILK super nodes are responsible to expanding the community, boosting the ecosystem, and improving the liquidation of Silk tokens. Applicators for becoming a SILK super node shall be mature enterprises or organizations with 3,000,000 Silk tokens purchased from the secondary market and hold for long-term. Hundreds of super nodes for different industries are planned by SilkChain.  2. Benefits  2.1 Free software + termed operation & maintenance service  The super node will have the ownership of different application software and rights of profit share of such.  2.2 Self-owned Community bonus share  The super node will have rights of sharing the Silk gas fee and the profit share of self-owned community operation.  What is the self-owned community? SilkChain has tailored independent platforms for each super node. Subject to this platform, there are Silk applications such as e-commerce, financing, gadget, as well as entertainment. Any user linked to these applications belongs to the self-owned community of that super node.  2.3 Extra bonus  When the applicator purchased Silk tokens from the public, the applicator will be rewarded with locked Silk tokens as a bonus at certain rates. The rate and unlock terms are related to the whole amount of the applicators holding tokens.  2.4 Task bonus  The super nodes will be rewarded with task bonuses at each milestone of task completion.  2.5 Referral bonus  The super nodes will be rewarded with referral bonus by succeeding introducing other applicators for super nodes.  2.6 Massive business opportunity  The super node will share massive information of suppliers and products for developing potential business in the SilkChain ecosystem.  3. Rights  3.1 Ownership of free software  3.2 Permission rights of subject nodes’ entry.  4. Decision-making Mechanism  Every Silk super node has the voting rights for adding & revising the mechanism, terms, and regulations of the Silk super nodes. Before the existence of 30 SILK super nodes, the International Trade Digitalization Commission (ITDC) has the final decision-making rights. After that, a decision-making committee will be elected under negotiation & voting of 30 SILK super nodes under supervision of ITDC and all members of the SilkChain ecosystem for each decision-making.  At present, there are 20 nodes have passed the first stage application. Among which, PT. Paloma Shopway has passed the verification and shall become the first super node, Silk Node — Paloma and execute with the rights and responsibilities of a super node very soon. Established in 2007, PT. Paloma Shopway is the largest home catalogue distributor with 340,000 memberships across Indonesia, covering the market of 10 millions of people and has annual turnover of USD 100 million.  Furthermore, 3 recognized enterprises has passed the final verification and queuing for becoming a SILK super node and 16 applicators are under verification successively. We are looking forward to every participant of international trade as trading companies, platforms, shopping malls, and cross-border e-commerce enterprises to join the SILK Super Node Election for more benefits of the SilkChain ecosystem.  If there is any update or change of SILK Super Node Election, SilkChain will be noticed on the three official channels: SilkChain Website, SilkAll Service Groups and Official Telegram Groups. Stay Tuned! Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: PT Paloma Shopway Becomes the First Global Super Node of SilkChain   As the first blockchain project dedicated to improving international trade and consumer spending ecosystem, SilkChain has launched SILK Super Node Election. The SILK super nodes are the high-level benefit owners of SilkChain’s ecosystem. In the mean time, the SILK super nodes are responsible to expanding the community, boosting the ecosystem, and improving the liquidation of Silk tokens. Applicators for becoming a SILK super node shall be mature enterprises or organizations with 3,000,000 Silk tokens purchased from the secondary market and hold for long-term.  At present, there are 20 nodes have passed the first stage application. Among which, PT Paloma Shopway has passed the verification and shall become the first super node, Silk Node — Paloma.  About Silk Node — Paloma  As the first super node, Silk Node — Paloma execute with the rights and responsibilities of a super node very soon. Founded in 2007, Paloma Shopway is the biggest home catalogue distribution enterprise in Indonesia. It has 340,000 members and 100,000 drop shippers. The main business of Paloma Shopway covers nearly 20 categories, such as: costume, luggage, shoes, home appliances and home furnishings. By means of displaying products on website, APP, regularly published product magazines and in offline experience stores, and selling products via telephone ordering, Paloma Shopway covers the market of 10 millions of people and has annual turnover of USD 100 million.  Now, Paloma Selection is a blockchain innovation project between Paloma and SilkChain in Indonesia. SilkChain implants Silk in Paloma commercial ecosystem with blockchain technology. Paloma members can earn Silk by online shopping, consumption and product reviews. At the same time, they can use Silk to participate VIP sales promotion, such as integral redemption, getting prizes, lottery and etc. Paloma can obtain big data through Silk’s circulation in system, and build the Southeast Asian consumer credit system. Based on the establishment of the credit system, SilkFinance service offers trade finance and any other supply-chain financial services, to help build the blockchain business ecosystem.  Hundreds of super nodes for different industries are planned by SilkChain. At the same time, SilkChain has launched application dividend plan. Any super node with the application system, the node project will provide the application dividend pools. As a form of “business and community alliance incentive”, the application dividend pools are used to accelerate the global implementation of the SilkChain ecological application, build an equal and mutually beneficial international trade ecology and share the huge dividends of ecological development. We are looking forward to every participant of international trade as trading companies, platforms, shopping malls, and cross-border e-commerce enterprises to join the SILK Super Node Election for more benefits of the SilkChain ecosystem.  As the Paloma Selection APP will online soon, Silk Node — Paloma will set sail for its first voyage for e-commerce with Silk Token economy. SilkChain will update every progress, please stay tuned! Body: SilkChain Received High Attention at Asean Blockchain Summit 2018  Asean Blockchain Summit 2018 has closed in Malaysia. This summit was organized by the Global Blockchain Foundation on September 3rd&4th, and the BLOCKCHAIN SUMMIT is the top class blockchain event series worldwide.  https://graph.baidu.com/resource/1c29dba3ca252245e50ba01536818384.jpg  In addition, Over 500 professionals and investors attended the summit, and there are many high-quality blockchain projects from all over the world. As the first blockchain project dedicated to improving international trade and consumer spending ecosystem, SilkChain was invited to attend this conference, and introduced the status of the project to all the guests at the conference. SilkChain received high attention from the participants and was widely recognized.  At the summit, the project leader introduced the project progress to all the guests present. He pointed out that SilkChain supports tens of thousands of overseas trade centers around the world to develop and use their own independent application Dapp.  The overseas trade center refers to the independent application scenario, establishes a credit investigation system based on its own system, and provides financial services to its members according to the credit records and value database. Finally, we will achieve global trade connectivity and establish the largest digital international trade community and international trade credit reporting system. At the same time, banks, insurance, logistics, payment and other third-party value-added services will also be stationed to provide international trade support services. Currently, based on the development of the silk chain, the world’s first cross-border e-commerce Dapp, e-dragon has been launched in Bahrain. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: Silk Trading in HitBTC Will be Available on 10 October!  As the first blockchain project dedicated to improving international trade and consumer spending ecosystem, SilkChain team has been confirmed that Silk will officially be available on the HitBTC exchange on Oct. 10, 2018.  HitBTC is one of the well-known exchanges, which has been established since 2013 and it is headquartered in Europe. HitBTC has been providing transaction service before the Bitcion had become popular and known as one of the exchanges creating growth opportunities for new coins and token. Most of the time the HitBTC’s trading volume is in the world’s top 5, and the website traffic rank in that of the global exchanges is in top 3. In addition, the exchange has been providing markets for digital assets, tokens and ICO as well as a wide range of available instruments and flawless uptime. HitBTC exchange has the features of high volume of transaction, reasonable fees, and high security, which will make the transaction more smooth and convenient. The advanced matching engine, the support of multi-token and the high quality service are attractive to the professional traders.  SilkChain will also push the process of listing on other exchanges. Meanwhile, in order to build an equal and mutually beneficial international trade ecology, achieve community prosperity, and share the huge dividends of ecological development with community users, SilkChain has released ecological incentive program and applications candy plan.  Ecological incentive program includes the token holder dividend incentive and operation incentive. Token holder dividend incentive is that all kinds of participants in the ecology have made outstanding contributions to the prosperity of SilkChain ecosystem during the construction process of SilkChain ecosystem. SilkChain will pay dividends to token holders according to the agreement in the white paper. Operation incentive, that is, all kinds of income generated by all kinds economic activities in SilkChain ecosystem will have corresponding incentive mechanism of distribution to each Token holder.  Applications candy plan is a bonus pool provided by SilkChain and its partners around the world after the implementation of the application. The trades who join in the Silk Tokenization plan will enjoy the benefits of traffic, transaction and supply chain for free, as well as the services of software and big data. Meanwhile, the project side will take a certain proportion of Silk as the airdrop candy pool to give back to Silk eco-users. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: Silk Will List on BitoPro Exchange Soon  The SilkChain team is thrilled to announce that Silk will be available on BitoPro exchange. BitoPro is a digital asset exchange targeting global investors that was established by BitoEX that has provided the Bitcoin trading service since 2014 so that users can buy Bitcoin from thousands of stores in Taiwan. BitoEX has established the BitoPro on the basis of the advantages of a large number of users, Bitcoin-selling stores and successful experience of operating Bitcoin wallets and other trading services in Taiwan.  BitoPro International Digital Asset Exchange is the biggest exchange in Taiwan and it can support fiat trading. BitoPro aims to establish a world-class blockchain asset exchange platform to provide global investors with a safer, more convenient, professional, trustworthy and excellent blockchain asset exchange service. In the future, BitoPro's business scope will include cryptocurrency and related derivatives trading services such as fiat trading, crypto-to-crypto trading, crypto-financing and leverage trading. BitoPro will also provide users with advanced digital asset management function, tools for risk management and platform-wide customer support, in order to meet each investor's investment needs. BitoPro focuses on the risk control and it has high level of stability. Meanwhile, BitoPro can provide the personalized services of AI Portfolio Digital Asset Management, Multi-Language Support, Multi-Platform Support and so on to meet the increasing market demand.  As the first project in the world that dedicates blockchain technology to improving international trade and consumer spending ecology, SilkChain represents the most powerful one initiated by the largest members among all crowd-funded blockchain projects until now. Recently, SilkChain has released New User Reward Program, Ecological Incentive Program and Applications Candy Plan. In the future, SilkChain will push the process of the economic design and construction of the Silk ecological community to build an equal and mutually beneficial international trade ecology, achieve community prosperity, and share the huge dividends of ecological development with community users. The BitoPro's advantages of high volume and all kinds of personalized services are consistent with the needs of the projects and community members.  BitoPro is one of many exchanges SilkChain will be working with and SilkChain will also push the process of listing on other exchanges. The updates about the listing date and the process of listing will be released through official website, SilkAll service groups and official telegram groups. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: SilkChain: It’s Time to Revolutionize International Trade! Did you know that the most “recent” innovation in international trade is actually CONTAINERS?” Mr. Yi Qing, CEO of SilkChain at the Mauritius Blockchain Conference during his speech. http://mt1.baidu.com/timg?shitu&quality=100&sharpen=100&er=&imgtype=0&wh_rate=null&size=h120&sec=1534388976&di=ac2e466b9ef791ac51299b0aad5a88d4&src=http%3A%2F%2Fa.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fimage%2F%2570%2569%2563%2Fitem%2Fb219ebc4b74543a90af2a6f813178a82b901141c.jpg It is an undeniable fact that international trade is one of the biggest industries of our time, well, not only our time as it has really been big since its inception 5 centuries ago. The UK, France and Holland were actually the first countries to “promote” this activity. When international trade started, it was meant to help potential traders find overseas markets, sell goods, find buyers, earn money and promote economic systems of their own countries. As much as we cannot deny that those advantages have been realisable, we can’t blind ourselves from the fact that there is lack of trust in the whole system; http://mt1.baidu.com/timg?shitu&quality=100&sharpen=100&er=&imgtype=0&wh_rate=null&size=h120&sec=1534389019&di=80bd4e1c28603928dd19fe136870f49d&src=http%3A%2F%2Ff.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fimage%2F%2570%2569%2563%2Fitem%2F3812b31bb051f81913d05f7ed7b44aed2e73e709.jpg “There is lack of trust in the system, especially in SME’s, as people do not trust each other generally. This is especially in SME’S as buyers and sellers, and traders and service providers do not trust each other at all.” Mr. Yi Qing, CEO of SilkChain in an exclusive interview with Decentral Magazine. So, what are the other major pain points in international trade? http://mt1.baidu.com/timg?shitu&quality=100&sharpen=100&er=&imgtype=0&wh_rate=null&size=h120&sec=1534389052&di=75d2640c97734589804a8ac8c5200d05&src=http%3A%2F%2Fg.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fimage%2F%2570%2569%2563%2Fitem%2F4afbfbedab64034f06f59d32a2c379310a551dcd.jpg  In 2017, the total trade volume of world merchandise was close to $32 trillion; a value equivalent to the sum of China and USA’s GDP. Even with this large number however, it is quite crucial to realise that from 2008-2017, the total growth of international trade has slowed down significantly. Apart from trust barriers, SME’s are also unable to get letters of credit, thus causing an immense trade problem. Due to the aforementioned reasons, SME’s face difficulties in establishing trust among cross-border merchants, thus, it becomes difficult to get large and highly efficient transactions. Secondly, it is difficult to introduce financial leverage to merchants as financial institutions have had a hard time in carrying out credit investigations among these people. In essence, the independent data structure, segregated data ownership, lack of publicly trustworthy safeguard mechanisms and a centralised IT system of the international trade industry are very fragmented. Consequently, there is no globally unified interconnection and there is definitely no trust whatsoever. But first, why is trade important? “China was very poor a long time ago, precisely, 30 years ago and the only prominent activity was agriculture. However, Chinese people started focusing on international trade and thus, many factories were set up at the coastal side of China. This activity provided jobs and attracted professional buyers from overseas, which made China richer. Moreover, manufacturers implemented technology and now, they have immense knowledge of the world and how to create such beneficial partnerships, thus international trade is very important for all developing countries.” Mr. Yi Qing, CEO of SilkChain in an exclusive interview with Decentral Magazine. Essentially, if developing countries want to follow China’s lead, then international trade is their best option. How is SilkChain Revolutionizing International Trade? SilkChain is the first ever blockchain project dedicated to improving the international trade ecosystem. Why silk? Well, because silk represented the common currency in ancient international trade. The blockchain technology is a good tool in solving the problems that exist in international trade. With that in mind, various major international business leaders headed by Osell Group, have come together to develop an organisation named International Trade Digitalization Commission (ITDC) with the purpose of making international trade seamless and empowering SME’s regarding this aspect. ITDC intends to use blockchain technology to promote DAO (Decentralized Autonomous Organization—a new generation of smart contract platform) within global industries, while experimenting in international trade. On top of its decentralized characteristic, the platform will promote global entities and simultaneously build a global merchant system. This will enable the platform to offer financial applications such as information storage, payment and liquidation, transparency within the supply chain, traceability and supply chain finance. The digital network platform is named SilkChain and the token issued is the Silk Token; which everybody can use through the various dApps available on the platform. With this technology, SilkChain will be able to increase efficiency and cut transaction costs within the international trading industry. So, what puts SilkChain at an advantage? “As a company from China, in the last 16 years, we have always worked on setting up a platform for international traders, which is why we have the experience, ecosystem and clients who we are transferring to the blockchain platform.” Mr. Yi Qing, CEO of SilkChain in an exclusive interview with Decentral Magazine. In essence, the team heading this has been in the international trade industry for 16 whole years, so they definitely know the ins and outs of this industry. Are there any challenges? According to Mr. Yi Qing, time is their biggest challenge. This is because Blockchain is growing fast and in China they say: “One day for blockchain, is equivalent to one day for other businesses.” He continued to mention that blockchain is the future and it grows really fast. This is also caused by the fact that they are trying to connect as many international traders as they can, thus they will be using a branch system, whereby they will create 400 nodes in the next three years, which is the main challenge. How big is their community? Thus far, they have 1 million people on Telegram and since China they use WeChat, they want to leverage it so that they get 10 million people in the next three years. It’s really great to see blockchain technology making a difference in regards to industries that have not innovated in the longest time. It would really be interesting to see how it all comes to play, considering that it is aimed at mostly developing countries where receptivity is still a bit of an issue. However, this is one use-case to truly look out for. This article is based on an exclusive interview between Decentral Magazine and Mr. Yi Qing of SilkChain during the Mauritius Blockchain Conference. This event took place on Monday, August 13th 2018 at the Intercontinental Hotel. Body: SilkChain R&D Progress [/b] August 6th, 2018 — August 12th, 2018 1. Support each DAPP technology development, including interface optimization. 2. Author: queena-silkchain
Title: join us and get bonus!-silkchain!
Body: SilkChain Application Scenarios Gained Wider Attention at Bahrain World Blockchain Congress      Yesterday, Bahrain World Blockchain Congress closed in Bahrain. It is reported that this summit was hosted by Central Bank of Bahrain and TRAICON EVENTS. Many government agencies have participated this summit, including Bahrain economic development committee, Bahrain blockchain management conference, Bahrain telecom authority, national petroleum and natural gas administration, Bahrain stock exchange and other government agencies.        At the summit, the project leader introduced the project progress to all the guests present. He pointed out that SilkChain supports tens of thousands of overseas trade centers around the world to develop and use their own independent application Dapp. The overseas trade center refers to the independent application scenario, establishes a credit investigation system based on its own system, and provides financial services to its members according to the credit records and value database. Finally, we will achieve global trade connectivity and establish the largest digital international trade community and international trade credit reporting system. At the same time, banks, insurance, logistics, payment and other third-party value-added services will also be stationed to provide international trade support services. Currently, based on the development of the silk chain, the world’s first cross-border e-commerce Dapp, e-dragon has been launched in Bahrain.      The organizer said that it is a great honor for the SilkChain to use Bahrain as a pilot application scenario, which will provide all-round support for the application scenario of the SilkChain project. It is expected that Bahrain will become a new starting point for a new international trade ecosystem reconstructed from the blockchain. Body: Hello,this is Silkchain App developer OSell Selection, today I am going to tell you about our SIlkchain based ecommerce app - OSell Selection.   Combining entertainment and e-commerce, OSell Selection provides SMEs, and buyers around the world a channel to buy directly from manufacturers. Not only can users find the best prices on this app through the use of blockchain technology, the App also ensures the authenticity and transparency of all the costs, and shipping information.   The app has 4 modules:arrow_right::arrow_right:: Preference, Winner, Silk Mining(Dig silk), and e-pet.   :one:Preference: this is where you can find the products selected by OSell, available at factory prices, without added margins from middlemen. Users can choose online payment or payment upon pickup from local service stations.   :two:Winner: Users can take part in treasure raid by paid for silk. After the raffle closes, the winner will be selected. The more entries you purchase, the higher the probability you will be the winner.   :three:Silk Mining(Dig silk): Complete certain tasks to receive energy through which you can obtain Silk.   :four:E-pet:You can upgrade the skills of pet. After the upgrade, it can unlock more skills, such as increased Silk reward for its work, take part in special Raider program, or battle other players for prizes and many other fun activities.
